HEADWORD: Infirmary
<hw>In*firm"a*ry</hw> <pr>(⟦icr⟧n*f⟦etil⟧rm"⟦adot⟧*r⟦ycr⟧)</pr>,
<pos>n.</pos>; <plu><it>pl.</it> <plw>Infirmaries</plw>
<pr>(-r⟦icr⟧z)</pr>.</plu> <ety>[Cf. OE. <ets>fermerie</ets>, OF.
<ets>enfermerie</ets>, F. <ets>infirmerie</ets>, LL.
<ets>infirmaria</ets>. See <er>Infirm</er>.]</ety> <def>A hospital, or
